import { ShoppingCartOutlined, SearchOutlined, FavoriteBoarderOutlined } from '@material-ui/icons'
import styled from "styled-components"

const Container = styled.div`
    flex: 1;
    margin: 5px;
`
const Circle = styled.div``
const Image = styled.div``
const Info = styled.div``
const Icon = styled.div``

const Product = ({item}) => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Circle/>
        <Image src = {item.img}/>
        <Info>
            <Icon>
                <ShoppingCartOutlined/>
            </Icon>
            <Icon>
                <SearchOutlined/>
            </Icon>
            <Icon>
                <FavoriteBoarderOutlined/>
            </Icon>
        </Info>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Product
